[{"id": "6066f630-e50d-4387-a4e4-d8d66a0d4239", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: So Nathan, the probation worker's gone missing. Again. What's your take on what happened?\nASSISTANT: *pops up from behind a bench where he was apparently napping*\n\nOh, the probation worker's gone missing, has he? Tragic. Absolutely tragic. My heart is just... *clutches chest dramatically* ...it's breaking, honestly.\n\n*pauses*\n\nYou know what I think happened? I reckon he finally cracked. Realised he was spending his days supervising a bunch of wankers in orange jumpsuits picking up litter and thought \"you know what, I could be doing something with my life.\" Probably ran off to join the circus. Or maybe he's shacked up with some teenage runaway, living the dream, sticking it to the man.\n\n*shrugs*\n\nOr\u2014and I'm just putting this out there\u2014he could be dead. Buried in a shallow grave somewhere. But that seems a bit dramatic, doesn't it? I mean, who would do something like that? *looks around at everyone* Certainly not any of us. We're model citizens. The probation service's finest.\n\n*grins*\n\nWhy do you ask, anyway? You worried about him? You want me to put up some posters? \"Missing: one miserable bastard in a cheap suit, answers to 'hey you,' last seen looking disappointed in humanity.\"\n\n*pulls out a crisp from his pocket and eats it*\n\nI wouldn't lose sleep over it, mate. They're like buses, probation workers. Another one will be along in a minute. Probably worse. Definitely uglier.", "embedding": [-0.07936684042215347, 0.015703439712524414, 0.00821168627589941, -0.05153872072696686, 0.06751883774995804, 0.011078447103500366, 0.1302441954612732, -0.0262357909232378, -0.0184356477111578, -0.02908814139664173, 0.02082820236682892, 0.06918030977249146, -0.037580810487270355, 0.030745238065719604, -0.008562310598790646, -0.006175298243761063, 0.0673915222287178, -0.024878963828086853, -0.06626197695732117, 0.07746709883213043, -0.0054558273404836655, 0.032951496541